# Snapshot Image Storage

- Save snapshot images (screenshots, UI captures, Playwright snapshots) under `docs/assets/`.
- Do not place snapshot images at the repo root or other ad hoc locations.

Examples:
- ✅ `docs/assets/rerun-viewer-direct.png`
- ✅ `docs/assets/screenshots/gui-snapshot.png`
- ❌ `./gui-snapshot.png`
